<a href="https://papygreek.com/text/1477">bgu.2.601</a>, l. 3
(Arsinoites, 101-200 CE).<br>
For more examples, see the <a data-link-newtab="" href="/search/180" data-url="search/180">search οι written instead of
ε</a>.</li>
<li>Nonstandard <strong>τίμερον</strong> &lt;timeron&gt; from standard
