<a href="https://papygreek.com/text/463990">t.varie.2</a>, l. 5 (Origin
not known, 601-700 CE)<br>
For more examples, see the <a data-link-newtab="" href="/search/181" data-url="search/181">search ε written instead of
οι</a>.</li>
</ul>
